{"title":"数据结构代码实现：队列的链式存储","uid":"c6398837a597d6503bc83e04065ac7ce","slug":"DataStructure-LinkQueue","date":"2020-05-12T01:21:11.000Z","updated":"2020-05-19T14:18:26.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/DataStructure-LinkQueue.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200512092935.png","content":"<h2 id=\"队列的链式存储的定义\"><a href=\"#队列的链式存储的定义\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"队列的链式存储的定义\"></a>队列的链式存储的定义</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#define ElemType int\ntypedef struct LinkNode&#123;\n    ElemType data;\n    struct LinkNode *next;\n&#125;LinkNode;\ntypedef struct &#123;\n    LinkNode *front,*rear;\n&#125;LinkQueue;</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"初始化队列\"><a href=\"#初始化队列\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"初始化队列\"></a>初始化队列</h2><ul>\n<li>创建头结点，使头指针和尾指针都指向头结点</li>\n<li>初始化为空<br><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200512095523.png\" alt=\"初始化队列\"><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">void InitQueue(LinkQueue &amp;Q)&#123;\n    Q.front&#x3D;Q.rear&#x3D;(LinkNode*)malloc(sizeof(LinkNode));&#x2F;&#x2F;创建头结点，使头指针和尾指针都指向头结点\n    Q.front-&gt;next&#x3D;NULL;&#x2F;&#x2F;初始化为空\n&#125;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"判队空\"><a href=\"#判队空\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"判队空\"></a>判队空</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">bool IsEmpty(LinkQueue Q)&#123;\n    return Q.front&#x3D;&#x3D;Q.rear;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"入队操作\"><a href=\"#入队操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"入队操作\"></a>入队操作</h2></li>\n<li>创建新的结点</li>\n<li>将数据填入结点</li>\n<li>将队尾指针的next指针指向s</li>\n<li>将rear指向s<br><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200512095525.png\" alt=\"入队操作\"><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">void EnQueue(LinkQueue &amp;Q,ElemType e)&#123;\n    LinkNode *s&#x3D;(LinkNode*)malloc(sizeof(LinkNode));&#x2F;&#x2F;创建新的结点\n    s-&gt;data&#x3D;e;&#x2F;&#x2F;将数据填入结点\n    s-&gt;next&#x3D;NULL;\n    Q.rear-&gt;next&#x3D;s;&#x2F;&#x2F;将队尾指针的next指针指向s\n    Q.rear&#x3D;s;&#x2F;&#x2F;将rear指向s\n&#125;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"出队操作\"><a href=\"#出队操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"出队操作\"></a>出队操作</h2></li>\n<li>判断队列是否为空</li>\n<li>非空，则将p指向头结点的下一个结点</li>\n<li>获取要出队的元素</li>\n<li>断链</li>\n<li>如果删除的是最后一个元素，将队列置为空</li>\n<li>释放内存<br><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200512095528.png\" alt=\"出队操作\"><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">bool DeQueue(LinkQueue &amp;Q,ElemType &amp;e)&#123;\n    if(IsEmpty(Q))&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;判断队列是否为空\n        return false;\n    &#125;\n    LinkNode *p&#x3D;Q.front-&gt;next;&#x2F;&#x2F;将p指向头结点的下一个结点\n    e&#x3D;p-&gt;data;&#x2F;&#x2F;获取要出队的元素\n    Q.front-&gt;next&#x3D;p-&gt;next;&#x2F;&#x2F;断链\n    if(Q.rear&#x3D;&#x3D;p)&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;删除的是最后一个元素\n        Q.rear&#x3D;Q.front;&#x2F;&#x2F;队列置为空\n    &#125;\n    free(p);\n    return true;\n&#125;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n","text":"队列的链式存储的定义#define ElemType int typedef struct LinkNode&#123; ElemType data; struct LinkNode *next; &#125;LinkNode; typedef struct &#123; Lin...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.3k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/categories/数据结构.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/tags/数据结构.json"},{"name":"C++","slug":"C","count":11,"path":"api/tags/C.json"},{"name":"考研","slug":"考研","count":11,"path":"api/tags/考研.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%98%9F%E5%88%97%E7%9A%84%E9%93%BE%E5%BC%8F%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">队列的链式存储的定义</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E5%8C%96%E9%98%9F%E5%88%97\"><span class=\"toc-text\">初始化队列</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%A4%E9%98%9F%E7%A9%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">判队空</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%85%A5%E9%98%9F%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">入队操作</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%87%BA%E9%98%9F%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">出队操作</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"CHEN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161140460.jpg","link":"/","description":"学无止境","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/cjpnice","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"数据结构代码实现：二叉树的遍历","uid":"395b448d9d7bd2d8a1561bdedabff9ce","slug":"DataStructure-BiTree","date":"2020-05-14T08:09:07.000Z","updated":"2020-05-19T14:18:09.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/DataStructure-BiTree.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200514161206.png","text":"二叉树的定义typedef char BiElemType; typedef struct BiTNode&#123; BiElemType data; struct BiTNode *lchild,*rchild; &#125;BiTNode,*BiTree; &#x2F;&#...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/categories/数据结构.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/tags/数据结构.json"},{"name":"C++","slug":"C","count":11,"path":"api/tags/C.json"},{"name":"考研","slug":"考研","count":11,"path":"api/tags/考研.json"}],"author":{"name":"CHEN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161140460.jpg","link":"/","description":"学无止境","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/cjpnice","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","jue